        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         ST has 2 effects<BR> <BR>1:  Mesmerize(1/55) <BR>2:  Memblur(1%) </P><P>I'm pretty sure the 1% means, 1% of the time, the memblur component activates.</P><P>If you ST a mob, at his spawn point, and FD before it wears off, he will always forget about you.  The Memblur component of ST rarely, if ever, takes hold.</P><P>Reepr<BR>Warlock of Lanys<BR><Sigil><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
