         Thanks for the feedback - one day into the guide and I have dinged 40 and well on way to 41. I also worked out that an fd after killing first mob and before going into aggro range of the st'ed 2nd mob would clear the aggro/hate list. But Im glad for the confirmation from my more experienced bretheren.</P><P>Retrevil - I have played the ping/pong with 2 mobs if the st fails - no need if I just forget to fd before pulling second mob as I just consider it a single pull and go into usual kill mode - as I havent drawn aggro while killing the 1st mob yet as I dont wander close enough to draw aggro - ie close to spawn point. The only ones I may have hassles with are pairs of casters nuking/dotting away while I get setup to fear/kite or several resists drawing aggro but not harming mob. Then its just a quick gate outside and reenter for a fresh approach.</P><P>Sarkoris<BR>Level 40 Iksar Necro</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
