         If ST lands on Mob.... 18 sec duration, and mem blur works if you are out of aggro range.....If it is not resisted both mez and blur work..... If you are in aggro range it will not forget you... unless: See below...</P><P>If you ST and then FD.... you will not have aggro as long as you do not get up from FD till after ST breaks...</P><P>Use this to break in LB in KC.... ST FD... I flip flop my way down that way.... Just doing FD does not work as they always seem to remember me when I get up...</P><P>Works for me everytime it sticks</P><P>Various Boneweiser<BR>Warlock of Cazic Thule<BR>Unruled Power<BR>Quellious</P><P>Edited by - Various B on 08/28/2002  10:09:02</P><P>Edited by - Various B on 08/28/2002  10:11:44<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
