        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Here's a little guide on how to do Nurga. I started at 35, and went to 45 there.</P><P>Basically, for each 2 spawn, if one is a caster, he's the one you pull first. Pull with invoke fear, FD right away. If FD fails, run around and FD. After you FD, wait for the other goblin to walk back to the spawn point, get up and kill the one you feared.</P><P>If both are casters, makes sure you time your FD so they're not casting a spell when you do it.</P><P>If both are casters and fear is resisted, either gate, or die hehe</P><P>In all the time 35-45, never had a situation where I couldn't break a spawn. As a last resort if FD fails or something, fear both of them and kill them both.</P><P>Necro on Vallon Zek<BR>There is no cow level.<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
